    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Until the spell ends, sleet falls in a 40-foot-tall, 20-foot-radius Cylinder centered on a point you choose within range. The area is &amp;Reference[heavilyobscured], and exposed flames in the area are doused.</p><p>Ground in the Cylinder is &amp;Reference[difficultterrain]. When a creature enters the Cylinder for the first time on a turn or starts its turn there, it must succeed on a Dexterity saving throw or have the &amp;Reference[prone] condition and lose &amp;Reference[concentration].</p>",
